<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
GnomeIconTextItem

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
Editable text canvas-item for icons. 

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
Provides a specialized canvas item for displaying icon captions which
can be interactively changed by the user.</para>

<para>This Canvas item is used by the <type>GnomeIconList</type> and
by the desktop icons provided by the GNOME file manager.</type>

